#sindhu_voice_assistant
-----------------------------------
voice assistant commands
--------------------------------
"who are you": tells information about voice assistant

"help":lists all commands

"change voice":used to change voice assistant voice to boy or girl

"bye bye":closes voice assistant
--------------------------------
voice commands
-------------------------------------

"volume up" or "unmute":increase your volume to maximum

"volume down" or "mute":mute your audio

"screenshot" or "snip": takes a screenshot of current screen

"desktop":takes you to desktop

"file explorer"or"my computer"or"this pc":takes you to files

"notepad":opens notepad

"switch tab":switches to recently opened application 

"shutdown":shutdowns your pc

---------------------------------------
opening an app
-----------------------------------------------

step 1 say "open"
step 2 specify app name:example-"calculator"
-------------------------------------------
typing with voice
----------------------------------------
say"type"
and say the things you want to type
to stop typing say "exit"
----------------------------------------
requirements
-------------------------------------
installation commands
python -m pip install pyaudio
python -m pip install pyautogui
python -m pip install pyttx3
python -m pip install SpeechRecognition



